Remarks. This species was recently described (Sychra in
Sychra et al . 2007
). Although its description is precise enough to recognize the species, the original drawings were published in such small size and low quality that it is difficult to accurately interpret some structures. Therefore, we included new drawings for this species in order to avoid misidentifications resulting from incorrect interpretations of the original illustrations. Furthermore, due to our finding of this louse species on host species other than the type host, we have provided some chaetotaxic and morphometric data separately for specimens from the other hosts.
